page.title: 02PEOPLE
page.content: From the 47 completed questionnaires that were returned to us we learned the following information about the people of Ireby. Total number of people accounted for on questionnaires:124. FEMALES:68 MALES:56 We broke this information down according to age and the results were as follows:-{ AGE GROUP. NUMBER OF PEOPLE 0 to 5 years. 6 6 to 11 years. 9 12 to 18 years. 6 19 to 25 years. 18 26 to 45 years. 32 46 to 65 years. 33 65 years on. 20 In the group of people aged 65 and up there were 13 women and 7 men, almost twice as many.
